description: The Sugarshack Sno-Mobile is serving up Florida's finest frozen treats, and so much more! New Orleans style Sno-Balls, Root Beer Floats with A&W;, Regular Ice Creams & Soft Serve Ice Cream, Old Fashioned Lemonade, Sweetened Ice Tea, Homestyle Cupcakes and cookies, and so much more are rolling up to a curb near you, thanks to this terrific truck. Don't miss out on this fantastic menu on the move, brought to you by The Sugarshack – Choose, Live, Be Happy!
name: The Sugarshack Sno Mobile & Dessert Truck
